<bibRefCitation author="Lasebikan" box="[424,804,1073,1098]" pageId="3" pageNumber="80" refString="Lasebikan, B. A., Betsch, J. - M. &amp; Dallai, R. (1980) A new genus of Symphypleona (Collembola) from West Africa. Systematic Entomology, 5, 179 - 183. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 3113.1980. tb 00407. x" type="journal article" year="1980">Lasebikan, Betsch &amp; Dallai, 1980</bibRefCitation>
